        { "ar": "اسْتَمَعَ", "tr": "istamaʿa", "en": "to listen (he listened)", "ex_ar": "اسْتَمَعَ إِلَى الأُغْنِيَة بِانْتِبَاه", "ex_en": "He listened to the song attentively." },
